{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-072","title":"Sentence 72","sectionId":"sentences-071","sectionTitle":"Sentence 71-80","pageStart":470,"pageEnd":475,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":53,"duplicateEntryCount":2,"pages":[{"number":470,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 72"},{"type":"text","text":"Even more shocking is the fact that the number and rate of"},{"type":"text","text":"imprisonment have more than doubled over the past twenty years, and"},{"type":"text","text":"recidivism—that is the rate for re-arrest—is more than 60 percent."},{"type":"text","text":"更让人吃惊的事实是，监禁的数目和比率在过去20年里翻了一"},{"type":"text","text":"番还有余，而累犯率，即再次逮捕的比率，高于60%。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句主干是Even more shocking is the fact。这个句子的表语even"},{"type":"text","text":"more shocking置于句首，在be动词之前，整句话是倒装句。在“the fact"},{"type":"text","text":"that ... more than 60 percent”中，第一个that引导同位语从句，解释说明"},{"type":"text","text":"the fact，同位语从句由and连接两个简单句，分别是“the number and rate"},{"type":"text","text":"... over the past twenty years”和“recidivism ... more than 60 percent”。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"imprisonment /ɪmˈprɪznmənt/ n. 关押，监禁","headword":"imprisonment"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 life imprisonment 终身监禁"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 imprison vt. 监禁"},{"type":"entry","text":"double /ˈdʌbl/ v. 加倍；是…的两倍 a. 两倍的","headword":"double"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 double agent 双重间谍"},{"type":"entry","text":"recidivism /rɪˈsɪdɪvɪzəm/ n. 再犯；累犯","headword":"recidivism"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 recidivist n. 惯犯；累犯者"}]},{"number":471,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"表示“非法暴力行为”的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"abet /əˈbet/ vt. 怂恿，教唆","headword":"abet"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 abet a crime 教唆犯罪"},{"type":"entry","text":"abuse /əˈbjuːs/ n. 虐待","headword":"abuse"},{"type":"text","text":"/əˈbjuːz/ vt. 虐待，伤害"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 child abuse 虐待儿童"},{"type":"entry","text":"arson /ˈɑːrsn/ n. 纵火","headword":"arson"},{"type":"entry","text":"assassin /əˈsæsn/ n. 刺客，暗杀者","headword":"assassin"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 assassinate vt. 暗杀"},{"type":"entry","text":"assault /əˈsɔːlt/ n./vt. 袭击","headword":"assault"}]},{"number":472,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 sexual assault 性侵犯"},{"type":"entry","text":"blackguard /ˈblækɡɑːrd/ n. 无赖，恶棍","headword":"blackguard"},{"type":"entry","text":"bloody /ˈblʌdi/ a. 血腥的","headword":"bloody"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 bloody battle 血战"},{"type":"entry","text":"detract /dɪˈtrækt/ v. 贬损，诋毁","headword":"detract"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 de（向下）+tract（拉）→向下拉→贬损"},{"type":"text","text":"drug traffic 毒品交易"},{"type":"entry","text":"felon /ˈfelən/ n. 重罪犯，恶棍","headword":"felon"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 felony n. 重罪"},{"type":"entry","text":"forcible /ˈfɔːrsəbl/ a. 强制的；暴力的","headword":"forcible"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 violent a. 暴力的"},{"type":"entry","text":"gangster /ˈɡæŋstər/ n. 歹徒，流氓；恶棍","headword":"gangster"},{"type":"entry","text":"heinous /ˈheɪnəs/ a. 十恶不赦的","headword":"heinous"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 heinous crime 滔天大罪"},{"type":"entry","text":"illegal /ɪˈliːɡl/ a. 不合法的，非法的","headword":"illegal"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 illegal act 不法行为"},{"type":"text","text":"illegal transaction 非法交易"},{"type":"entry","text":"implicate /ˈɪmplɪkeɪt/ vt. 牵连","headword":"implicate"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 implicate in 使卷入…"},{"type":"text","text":"joint offense 共同犯罪"},{"type":"entry","text":"malefactor /ˈmælɪfæktər/ n. 罪犯；作恶者","headword":"malefactor"},{"type":"entry","text":"malice /ˈmælɪs/ n. 恶意；预谋","headword":"malice"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 malice aforethought 恶意预谋"},{"type":"entry","text":"maltreat /ˌmælˈtriːt/ vt. [书面语]虐待","headword":"maltreat"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 maltreatment n. 虐待"}]},{"number":473,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"mayhem /ˈmeɪhem/ n. 重伤罪","headword":"mayhem"},{"type":"entry","text":"murder /ˈmɜːrdər/ n./vt. 谋杀","headword":"murder"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 mass murder 大屠杀